title: A Young Auntie
description: Lee Minhyuk used to be a national Taekwondo fighter. However, he retired after suffering an injury. On a particular day, a young girl, named Narae, appears in front of him. Compared to her younger self, she has transformed into a grown woman and happens to dorm with Minhyuk. However, on the first dorm night, he was caught having sex by the auntie, and...
author: Saekma Shingong
